Titolo: Yoshi's Crafted World

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Yoshi's Crafted World is a side-scrolling platform video game developed by Good-Feel and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo Switch. The eighth main installment in the Yoshi franchise, the game was revealed at E3 2017, and was released worldwide on March 29, 2019. The game received generally positive reviews from critics and sold 1.11 million copies worldwide in three days, making it one of the best-selling games on the system. The game follows the Yoshis as they venture to collect the scattered gems of the Sundream Stone, which has the ability to grant wishes, before Kamek and Baby Bowser can.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
